transcript:
[Ringing]
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Haan Varun sahab. Awaz aa rahi hai?
Customer: Haan ji sir, mere paas patient hai, maine aapko kaha na, main karta hoon patient se free hoke main aapko call back karta hoon.
Executive: Achcha achcha, theek hai sir.
Customer: Haan ji. Theek hai sir.
summary:
Concerns:

- Customer has a patient and will call back later.



Resolution:

- Executive agreed to wait for the callback.



Next Steps: 

Issue not resolved. Customer will call back after attending to the patient.



Alert (If Any):

None

@@@Sentiment:

Neutral to neutral



@@@Key Topics:

callback, patient
